, media competence, communication training, developmental dyslexia, the treatment of stuttering, and the description of language disorders.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aAngewandte Linguistik. 4aInteraktion. 4aKognition. 4aKommunikative Kompetenz. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aApplied linguistics.  aintrapersonal communication.  alanguage and social interaction.  asocial cognition.1 aRickheit, Gert, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aStrohner, Hans, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)z978311023845708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015z978311074296108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2008z9783110212129oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2008z978311021213608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2008z9783110209457oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978311018829540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311019900040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110199000423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110199000/original  a978-3-11-021213-6  E-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2008b2008  a978-3-11-023845-7  DGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PA